                "SI",
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " reaction products were detected",
                "by an two arrays of dE-E Si telescopes. The telescopes",
                "consisted of 20 to 25 mu-m Si dE detectors backed",
                "by 300 mu-m thick Si E detector."
              ]
            }
